Sentencas: The effect of the Pt film thickness, in the range between 0.5 mu m and 9 mu m, on the polarization characteristics of the anode in a H-2-H2O gas mixture was studied using a fixed film Pt electrode at around 1273 K.
Titulo: Effect of film thickness on the polarization characteristics of a Pt anode on zircona electrolyte

Sentencas: The smaller interface resistance and the smaller DC overvoltage were obtained from the thinner Pt film.
Titulo: Effect of film thickness on the polarization characteristics of a Pt anode on zircona electrolyte

Sentencas: It was considered that the effect of the Pt film thickness is due to structural change of the Pt film with the thickness based on a model fitting.
Titulo: Effect of film thickness on the polarization characteristics of a Pt anode on zircona electrolyte

Sentencas: The anodic current was proportional to P-H2(1/4) but not affected by P-H2O.
Titulo: Effect of film thickness on the polarization characteristics of a Pt anode on zircona electrolyte
